1 ansible shell vs ansible command module
2
3 shell module
4 command module
5
6 shell module --> it will use shell environment, means we can use redirections >, pipes | and other shell variables I
7
8 command module --> it will just run the commands, but can't use shell environment like > pipe | or variables.

if a simple plain command with out variables, redirections, pipes, etc. we can use command module..

if you want to run shell script inside ansible or complex commands with redirections then we can use shell module